%N A394751 Numbers k such that sigma(k) = psi(k) + tau(k) + Omega(k)^4.
%e A394751 5375 is a term since sigma(5375) = 6864 = 6600 + 8 + 4^4 = psi(5375) + tau(5375) + Omega(5375)^4.
%o A394751 (PARI) isok(k) = {my(f = factor(k)); sigma(f) == prod(i=1, #f~, (f[i, 1]+1) * f[i, 1]^(f[i, 2]-1)) + numdiv(f) + bigomega(f)^4; } \\ _Amiram Eldar_, Mar 31 2026
